  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK902">
<l>pēṇātu peṇviḻaivā ṉākkam periyatōr </l>
<l>nāṇāka nāṇut tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth of him who, regardless (of his manliness), devotes himself to his wife's feminine nature will cause great shame (to ali men) and to himself;</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
